Crypto stuff in hpoa is dependent on libcrypt of openssl-1.0.1u.tar.gz
libcrypt needs fips support so also need openssl-fips-2.0.13.tar.gz

configure openssl-fips:
./config --prefix=/home/marcelw/ia64/src/C/ssl/fips-2.0 --openssldir=/home/marcelw/ia64/src/C/ssl/fips-2.0 shared
make
make install


configure openssl:
 ./config --prefix=/home/marcelw/ia64/src/C/ssl/openssl --openssldir=/home/marcelw/ia64/src/C/ssl/openssl fips shared
Need to edit the Makefile so FIPSDIR and FIPSLIBDIR point to the correct folder
make
make install
